description: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleader Abby Summers' viral TikTok revealed the laborious process of preparing pom-poms, sparking fan outrage. Viewers criticized the multi-billion dollar organization for expecting cheerleaders to perform such tasks themselves, drawing parallels to football players receiving equipment support. The discussion highlights the often-unseen labor behind the iconic cheer squad.
title: Dallas Cowboys cheerleader sparks debate with shocking pom-pom rule

description: Blake Lively is reportedly anxious about her career following a supposed rift with close friend Taylor Swift. Sources suggest Lively fears Swift's significant influence in Hollywood could impact her professional future. Despite attempts to reconcile, Lively is said to be struggling with the silence from Swift, who has yet to address the alleged fallout publicly.
title: 'She’s really scared': Taylor Swift’s behavior leaves Blake Lively worried about future
